      "title": "Companies allowed to pay in USD to get weekly fuel quota",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); The Minister of Energy, Kanchana Wijesekara says that any company or an industry which can pay in US Dollars can open a consumer account at CPC to obtain a weekly guaranteed quota.",
        "According to the Minister, the relevant companies or industries are required to pay a month in advance, and fuel will be issued on a daily or weekly basis from 12th July.",
        "Customers who have already paid will receive their quota from 12th of July, the Minister adds."
      ],
